text:
you can do it adding an extra class inside where you generate that topic menu. probably the submenu is generated with a for like:
{% for topic in topic_list %}
&lt;a href="{{topic.slug}}"&gt;{{topic.name}}&lt;/a&gt;
...
So you can use:
{% if topic == "topic.slug "%}

the final should be:
&lt;a href="{{topic.slug}}" {% if topic == topic.slug %}&gt;{{topic.name}}&lt;/a&gt;
class="active"
{% endif %}
